{
  "name": "Familiar - Pact of the Chain Master",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "/systems/dnd5e/icons/spells/wild-eerie-2.jpg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div title=\"Page 1\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p><span style=\"color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">Familiar is infused with a measure of its master's eldritch power, granting the following benefits:</span></p>\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813; font-size: 13px;\">\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">The familiar gains either a <strong>flying speed </strong>or a s<strong>wimming speed</strong> (master's choice) of <strong>40 feet.</strong></li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">As a<strong> bonus action</strong>, the master can command the familiar to take the <a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\" href=\"https://www.dndbeyond.com/compendium/rules/basic-rules/combat#Attack\" data-tooltip-href=\"//www.dndbeyond.com/actions/1-tooltip?disable-webm=1&amp;disable-webm=1\">Attack</a>&nbsp;action.</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">The familiar&rsquo;s<strong> weapon attacks are considered magical </strong>for the purpose of overcoming immunity and resistance to nonmagical attacks.</li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">If the familiar forces a creature to make a saving throw, it <strong>uses its master's spell save DC.</strong></li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">When the familiar takes damage, the master can use its <strong>reaction</strong> to grant the familiar <strong>resistance</strong> against that damage.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>FoundryVTT:&nbsp;</strong>Only the saving throw element is automated. Remaining effects to be handled manually.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
